Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:09.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:20.33,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.51,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:06.98,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:14.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:20.99,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:28.44,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:37.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Retreat at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that the enemy Simouns\Nshowed up in battle today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:12.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a taunt to let us know\Nthey can attack us at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly\Nwhat they're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.54,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Eternal Maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's really over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,So now we can finally devote our\Nlives to just offering prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is it that it doesn't\Nmake us feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see that other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that Grandpa was\Nalways yearning to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different world than this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I became a sibylla,\Nso I could get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Comment: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean that Amuria\Nmay also be alive somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vice Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:05:00.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please don't call me that.\NThat is no longer my title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:06.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Though its life may have ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:10.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this flower can still\Nprovide solace at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:20.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you attend the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that means it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still provide solace, did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I no longer have the power to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can no longer protect my Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the two conditions set by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Shoukoku and the Plumbum highlands\Nin exchange for the ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever thought to inform me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:56.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're to be treated as their\Nequals, if only on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And just whose doing would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,"War is foolishness..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military governors from\NPlumbum and Shoukoku have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, we have been waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really how\Nthings should turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was for the sibyllae\Nto continue praying to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with this change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way the high priestess\Nwas acting just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are they still around when\Nthe peace ceremony is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:14.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard that some of their forces\Nare staying on the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think of it, the less I\Nunderstand what this "peace" is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:26.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until they found the ancient Simouns,\Nit was their comrades who were dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is what they\Nlook like in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,All those faces that we\Nextinguished with our Ri Majons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We never even knew\Nwhat they looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they didn't know what\Nwe looked like either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the food's\Ngetting cold. Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Roatreamon, have some of my fish.
Comment: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're getting too thin, you know!\NYou have to get more nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura, you sound like her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your legs are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get those filthy legs\Nof yours out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know you can't understand\Na word I'm saying, but...
Comment: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? I see that you\Nknow I'm insulting you!
Comment: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:22.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Comment: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Comment: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us,\NSibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have committed an unspeakable sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bless you. Go in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bless us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bless you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're in the shower too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, yours are pretty huge, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Because you're\Ngoing to become a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become a man, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become strong, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can never protect what's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know what? Neviril\Ntold me something once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:58.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,To become strong by being held...\NYou're wrong about that, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's only when you've\Nboth become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that you can truly\Nhold each other close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I always thought I wanted\Nto become a man too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now I think I can manage\Nwithout making that change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should accept yourself as you\Nare. Your life will be easier then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you were at the Ruins,\Nso how in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you believed that to be true,\Nthen why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is an extremely\Nunstable place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:32.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins served as the\Ntraining grounds for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,So many abortive Emerald Ri Majons\Nexploded into oblivion there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are believed to\Nmanipulate time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,And because of this, Space\Nand Time were distorted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:54.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...causing the Spring to exist\Nsimultaneously in two different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I find all of this hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:04.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are very few things that\Npeople can actually believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:10.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...when they are unable\Nto believe in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:23.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be near my comrades\Nwho had fallen in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...yet I was also trying to flee\Nas far away from them as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I was the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I shied away from making a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and tried to run as far\Naway from reality as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I've been seeking\Nyou out all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to have someone hear my confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,To hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...my sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,One of the conditions of our peace\Ntreaty with Plumbum and Shoukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...calls for the\Ndissolution of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where did Yun run off\Nto at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want any part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest, disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all the effort we\Nput into it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Plumbum priestesses will be\Ntaking over our duties, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm confused. Is this what peace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can never hope to be on equal terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:02.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,One thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:10.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,They have no use for\Nus anymore. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when we finally\Nstarted to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the true meaning of\Nour prayers as sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even after Chor Tempest\Nceases to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:31.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...nothing can change the fact\Nthat we're all Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:37.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,And nobody will ever debase our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Chor Tempest is disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we won't be able to\Nfly the Simouns anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to that other world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will be closed to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've always longed to see\Nthat other world, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you being so talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't talked like\Nthis in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:58.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you give me your blessing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Sulking, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight with Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you\Nasking me about Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right on the money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,She talks up a storm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you can always use\Nyour mouth to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boy, kissing is all you\Never think about, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me it's when you really like\Nsomeone that you want to kiss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,So don't you want to kiss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not the way Neviril is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you like her anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I feel hot all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, you're in critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold up! What do you mean, critical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,It might not just be Neviril, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It could be that you've\Nchanged as well, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:56.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is Sibylla Aer? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it, High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose you'll do, Sibylla\NParaietta. Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me. Please. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must take off now, Sibylla\NParaietta, Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose! You must\Ngo at once! If you don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:30.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the door will close on us!\NNever to open again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I was a member of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamed of completing\Nthe Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamed of becoming an eternal maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun is much like a maiden herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maiden vacillates...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun gem reflects\Nthat vacillating soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maiden drifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Escaping reality for all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tracing the skies with\Nher everlasting beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please slow down, Your Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must change Kyuukoku's fate!\NWe cannot go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless we do something about it, we...
Comment: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Comment: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! You must go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the Land of Hope!
Comment: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Comment: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Comment: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:24.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're keeping something\Nfrom me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,As your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,When one flees from reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...refusing to choose a gender...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this is what becomes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:47.85,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.10,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:59.14,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:06.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.64,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:24.82,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:32.82,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:44.24,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:47.67,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:53.34,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:59.58,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:10.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril bares her soul to Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:13.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the other sibyllae make\Ntheir way towards the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:18.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Choices.
